  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] What I'm able to add to that-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] well, this is where we stand.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I hope now that I'll be able to play for you some of this works written by these composers.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I would like to play one I just call 'In Memoriam' [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] by [PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] Ben Susam, Menachem Ben Susam.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And after that, perhaps one other little piece called Horah, built in old Biblical form Horah, dance form, a very brilliant piece, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] both, both of them built in the Biblical chants.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Of course, at various time I have a number of other things that I would like to play.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I-- unfortunately, many of them are with piano.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "That perhaps for one better opportunities, we'd be able to perform them also and make one recordings with them.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[SIGHS] Of course, [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] the effects of, of my childhood over my life was very depressing.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This is a fact that's always remain as one very deep scar in my head.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Fortunately enough, this wound, it was [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] imposed, provoked in my, in my life was not a fatal one totally to destroy it.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And first of all, fortunately, I'm able-- I'm alive, able just to speak and recollect everything what was happening.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But what I'm very glad is that this [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] left enough straight in order that I start to appreciate it in one different way much deeper.",
      "word_count": 29
    }
  ],
